Package photos.app

Class Photos

java.lang.Object
javafx.application.Application
photos.app.Photos
public class Photos
extends javafx.application.Application
Photos is the class which starts and runs the application. It knows which user is currently logged in, if any, and provides methods to direct the user to the different pages in the application.
Author:
Robert Kulesa, Aaron Kan
